            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1624611072568-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1/2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot add the <strong>chicken breast strips</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 8-10 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
